# Hello

A simple Hello World Gem with spanish support, written by Mert AKSOY

## Installation

Download the Project and build a gem:

	gem build hello.gemspec


install it yourself as:

	gem install hello-0.0.1.gem

and use it

## Usage

	$ irb
	>>require 'hello'
	=> true
	>>Hello.hi
	=>Hello world!
	>>Hello.hi("spanish")
	=>hola mundo

